      of the Internet. To connect, you'll need to run an IRC client on
      your computer and use this connection information:</p>

      <div class="connection-info">
        Server: <em>chat.freenode.net</em><br>
        Channel: <em>#meteor</em>
      </div>

      <p>If you don't have an IRC client yet,
