        set up. You can also connect to IRC <a href="https://webchat.freenode.net/">in your browser</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Tips for using IRC</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><em>Check <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/meteor?sort=newest&pagesize=15" target="_blank">Stack
